# On the source computer, open Terminal and run:\nscp -r /Users/sourceusername/Library/Application\ Support/iPhone\ Simulator/User/Applications/<GUID> destinationusername@destinationcomputer:/path/to/destination\n\n# You will need to replace "sourceusername" with your actual username on the source machine,\n# "destinationusername" with the appropriate username on the target machine,\n# and "/path/to/destination" with where you want the folder copied to.